29:56.010 --> 29:56.840
- Ada.

29:58.370 --> 30:00.090
- Your windows could use a new coat.

30:01.300 --> 30:02.490
- Yeah.

30:02.540 --> 30:05.020
Every day I tell my husband to fix them.

30:06.500 --> 30:08.000
- Sorry, I can't help myself.

30:09.030 --> 30:12.700
This place needs some work.

30:12.750 --> 30:13.580
It's what I do.

30:15.250 --> 30:16.480
Really?

30:16.530 --> 30:17.360
- Yeah.

30:18.440 --> 30:19.820
Civil engineer by trade.

30:20.760 --> 30:21.590
- All right.

30:23.640 --> 30:25.680
We need a contractor for the summer.

30:25.730 --> 30:27.690
We're turning it into a BnB.

30:31.130 --> 30:34.160
- My older daughter,
Adrienne, is our designer.

30:35.310 --> 30:36.140
- Great.

30:38.220 --> 30:39.220
Beautiful & smart.

30:40.700 --> 30:43.310
- Well, let me show you the house.

30:46.500 --> 30:48.210
This home means a lot to me.

30:49.230 --> 30:50.620
