31:14.950 --> 31:16.230
- Are you tired, sweetie?

31:16.280 --> 31:17.710
- Where's daddy?

31:19.570 --> 31:20.850
- Daddy's at home, baby.

31:23.630 --> 31:25.040
You'll see him after summer.

31:25.090 --> 31:27.280
- He doesn't wanna be with us?

31:28.250 --> 31:29.250
- No, no, no.

31:29.300 --> 31:31.450
It's not that, sweetie.

31:31.500 --> 31:36.500
It's just, I wanted to spend some time

31:36.760 --> 31:39.240
because after this summer

31:42.540 --> 31:46.670
mummy's going away for a
little while and I'll miss you.

31:48.100 --> 31:49.020
I'm so sorry.

31:49.070 --> 31:51.100
