- We're practically having sex.

48:17.090 --> 48:17.940
Let's just do it.

48:20.120 --> 48:23.540
All right.

48:25.800 --> 48:26.600
- "He's an animal.

48:26.650 --> 48:28.160
He has an animal's habits."

48:32.620 --> 48:33.820
- Whenever you're ready.

48:39.640 --> 48:40.430
- "How much does it

48:40.480 --> 48:41.850
cost for these furs?

48:45.890 --> 48:48.840
- Those were a tribute
from an admirer of mine."

48:57.750 --> 48:58.590
Oh, I...

49:01.110 --> 49:01.940
Oh.

49:03.960 --> 49:06.020
- I acted like a dick before.

49:06.070 --> 49:07.380
I'm sorry.

49:07.430 --> 49:08.950
- You did.

49:09.000 --> 49:10.300
- We had a bit of a fight.

49:11.580 --> 49:12.410
People do that.

49:14.050 --> 49:15.390
Right?
- I guess.

49:20.060 --> 49:22.210
- Do you know what else people do?

49:54.460 --> 49:55.490
- Sorry.

49:55.540 --> 49:56.630
I'm so sorry.

50:10.510 --> 50:12.930
So, I hope everything's okay.

50:14.660 --> 50:16.030
I know you're in good hands,

50:16.080 --> 50:19.480
but it would have been nice,

50:19.530 --> 50:21.310
really nice if you showed up.

50:25.610 --> 50:26.660
Did you go get drunk?

50:28.350 --> 50:30.100
- I'll learn to kiss you better.

50:30.150 --> 50:32.760
- Well, right timing,
that's the first thing.

50:36.210 --> 50:37.500
You were beautiful.

50:40.260 --> 50:42.260
I missed the end of the match to be here.

50:43.560 --> 50:46.480
- Well, that's very kind of, honey.

51:11.860 --> 51:13.660
- You look beautiful in the morning.

51:17.970 --> 51:21.720
“A confetti carnival in my head
I ponder it all as I lay in bed”

51:42.330 --> 51:43.820
Let’s go?

51:43.870 --> 51:44.840
On... y?

51:44.890 --> 51:47.120
I have to
be back in the afternoon.

51:48.350 --> 51:49.180
- Me too.

51:51.750 --> 51:53.650
I'm meeting with your sister actually.

51:58.680 --> 52:02.100
We're already Monday...

52:03.750 --> 52:04.580
- What?

52:08.790 --> 52:11.640
Adrienne, I
don't see any progress

52:11.690 --> 52:12.770
with the deck at all.

52:13.800 --> 52:15.770
